com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.scriptItem

Class StoreItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.scriptItem.StoreItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ScriptItem

    public class StoreItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements ScriptItem
    A StoreItem consist of a variableName and a value, which gets stored in the DataStorage in Context.getDataStorage(). However, the value gets resolved before it is stored.
